WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
[Music]

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Jewish life at Cal Poly — a story of identity and belonging.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Chabad at Cal Poly, also known as the Rohr Center for Jewish Life,
provides a home away from home for Jewish students.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Each week, students gather for Shabbat dinner — sharing food,
tradition and community.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:26.000
"Chabad plays a really big role in my life.
I've met some of my best friends in college."

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.000
For many students, it's a place where identity is shared
and belonging comes naturally.
